    {
      "id": "PopularPost60737",
      "post_content": "There's definitely better ways to lock out your opponent. [Curse of chains](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Curse of chains) for instance, if you're sticking with U/W. But this does give you the option to tap enemy creatures without losing a card, so if you've got some combo going with tapping their creatures, could work well. 3.5/5",
      "posted_by": "Creyn",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost60737\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">There's definitely better ways to lock out your opponent. <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Curse of chains\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Curse of chains\">Curse of chains</a> for instance, if you're sticking with U/W. But this does give you the option to tap enemy creatures without losing a card, so if you've got some combo going with tapping their creatures, could work well. 3.5/5</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '60737'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy31505\">Creyn</span>\r\n                                (3/19/2010 8:27:03 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"